description: What could be better than a New York-style hot dog like the Beer Kraut, Grilled Onions crowned “Bababooey” or the creamy slaw, pickle- topped “Commish”? Poor Huey’s, doesn't think there’s much that can compare. This great hot dog cart is putting a Cajun kick on this street food favorite - the menu includes many unique combinations of flavorsm from New York to Nawlin’s. Check out these Real, Natural Casing, Bronx Style Hot Dogs!
name: Poor Huey's
